# concepts/ starts empty
#
# One file per term whose meaning you want to lock down — your work vocabulary.
# Filename = the term, slugified. Example: relative-strength.md
#
# Ask Claude: "Add a concept entry to brain/concepts/ for {term}. Define it in my
# words, note where I keep relearning it, add [[wikilinks]] to projects/patterns
# that use it."
#
# This .gitkeep exists only so the empty folder survives a git clone. Delete it
# once you have real entries.
